*nikola-7.8.9 (20 Jun 2017)

  20 Jun 2017; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -nikola-7.8.6.ebuild, -nikola-7.8.7.ebuild,
  +nikola-7.8.9.ebuild:
  Add version 7.8.9, delete old version 7.8.6 and 7.8.7

  15 Jun 2017; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.8.8.ebuild:
  Add more note for python_targets_python3_5

  15 Jun 2017; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.7.8.ebuild, nikola-7.8.6.ebuild,
  nikola-7.8.7.ebuild, nikola-7.8.8.ebuild:
  dev-python/ghp-import should be >=0.4.1-r1

   dev-python/ghp-import-0.4.1 has a bug about UTF-8 encordings.
  dev-python/ghp-import-0.4.1-r1 fixes this bug.

   Upstream is fixed as of version 0.5.0
   cf. https://github.com/davisp/ghp-import/commit/9b6311

   Note:
    Nikola prefers ghp-import2 to ghp-import
    https://github.com/getnikola/nikola/commit/7f7f660

  15 Jun 2017; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.8.6.ebuild, nikola-7.8.7.ebuild,
  nikola-7.8.8.ebuild:
  Now, dev-python/doit has [python_targets_python3_5]

