*nikola-7.7.8 (07 Jun 2017)

  07 Jun 2017; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +nikola-7.7.8.ebuild:
  Revert version 7.7.8 deletion

   As of as of 2017-06-06,
  =dev-python/ws4py-0.3.4 is newest in gentoo repository,
  >=www-apps/nikola-7.7.9[websocket] can't be installed because of version
  deps

   And licenses/Gutenberg is needed for this 7.7.8

  cf.
   - https://github.com/getnikola/nikola/blob/v7.7.8/requirements-extras.txt
   - https://github.com/getnikola/nikola/blob/v7.7.9/requirements-extras.txt

